    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials Section -->
    <section class="container mb-5">
        <h2 class="section-title">Community Voices</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="testimonial text-center">
                    <img src="/assets/imgs/testimonials/david.jpg" alt="David Chen" onerror="this.classList.add('error')">
                    <p class="testimonial-text">"EduSign transformed my life. As a deaf student, I struggled in traditional classrooms. Here, I found resources tailored to my needs and a community that understands. Now I'm thriving in college and planning to become a sign language interpreter."</p>
                    <p class="testimonial-author">David Chen</p>
                    <p class="testimonial-role">College Student</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="testimonial text-center">
                    <img src="/assets/imgs/testimonials/maria.jpg" alt="Maria Lopez" onerror="this.classList.add('error')">
                    <p class="testimonial-text">"As a parent of a deaf child, I was overwhelmed until I found EduSign. The resources here helped our whole family learn sign language together. My daughter now has the confidence to express herself and is excelling in school."</p>
                    <p class="testimonial-author">Maria Lopez</p>
                    <p class="testimonial-role">Parent</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="testimonial text-center">
                    <img src="/assets/imgs/testimonials/james.jpg" alt="James Wilson" onerror="this.classList.add('error')">
                    <p class="testimonial-text">"Being born deaf in a hearing world was challenging. Through EduSign, I've connected with mentors who guided me through college and into my career. Now I work as a software engineer and mentor others in the community."</p>
                    <p class="testimonial-author">James Wilson</p>
